  "title": "Joint probabilistic projection of female and male life expectancy",
  "abstract": "We find that the average gap between female and male life expectancy has been increasing for female life expectancy below 75, and decreasing for female life expectancy above 75. Our projections of the gap are lower than the UN's 2008 projections for most countries and so lead to higher projections of male life expectancy.",
